data.description: Outstanding value for this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom manufactured home on 1.72 acres with a superb location and picturesque countryside vistas! Recent updates include HVAC, water heater & dishwasher.  Enjoy the spacious back deck and yard with lots of mature tree. Nestled in a serene country setting yet conveniently close to the city, this property backs up to expansive acreage. City water, sewer, and trash pick-up add to the amenities. Bring your loved ones and pets to savor the joys of country living just minutes from town!
